Comment.val: /*fetches product possession details list of a party for a certain period of time*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT h.id , h.changedate, h.ppr_id FROM productpossession_hist_hd_vw h WHERE h.ppr_id IN ( SELECT DISTINCT (h.ppr_id) FROM productpossession_hist_dt d, productpossession_hist_hd h WHERE d.pphh_id =h.id AND d.party_id=:1) AND h.changedate <=TO_DATE(':2', 'yyyymmdd') ORDER BY h.ppr_id , h.changedate DESC
